<p>Joomlart broke new ground in the Joomla! community by unveiling <strong>JA Elastica</strong>, the <strong>FIRST</strong> Joomla! template with a <strong>Responsive Web Design and as our gift to the community, we offer it FREE! for all. Support forums are however restrcited to paid active members only.</strong> </p>

<p>JA Elastica truly is one template to serve all.  With its exclusive Responsive coding, JA Elastica adapts and transforms to fit the screen area of any device - be it a 30 inch extra wide monitor to the smallest iPhone screen.

<p>The template uses the <a href=”http://masonry.desandro.com/”>jQuery Masonry script</a>.
<p>This template does not support RTL CSS style</p>

